ActOperational Service Medal Regulations
SubjectOrder Awarding the Operational Service Medal With the EXPEDITION Ribbon
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-1098 of September 2, 2010; (2) determining the eligibility criteria worthy of recognition by the award of the Operational Service Medal with the EXPEDITION ribbon; (3) specifying the appearance of the EXPEDITION ribbon; and (4) establishing the order of precedence of the Operational Service Medal with the EXPEDITION ribbon in the Canadian Honours System.
